{"tid":738520,"cid":35,"subCid":0,"title":"自由鳥定SUN MOBILE","createTime":"2018-07-11T14:48:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-16T04:03:01.000Z","uid":132140,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"6168a40e223d5918508c9235306a9fd5616ed75a","tid":738520,"uid":132140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T14:48:05.000Z","msg":"原本用緊CMHK  5GB無限 然後爆咗就限速。<br />\n但撘西鐵用真係好垃圾⋯完全用唔到<br />\n然後我個plan $208 ，屋企1gb $160<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n10月就到期，見好多人都用SUN MOBILE OR 自由鳥。<br />\n<br />\n其實返工都好少真係不停用電話，返到屋企都轉返用寬頻。<br />\n所以我都係求撘車，岀街 上到網但又唔洗load 空氣。<br />\n<br />\n唔好同我講轉用儲值卡，我用咗個號碼好耐，點都一定要係攜號。<br />\n<br />\n你哋點睇？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Sun Mobile <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自由鳥"},{"pid":"e6f18554414412e0ddb703e6c0972cc5ad04fcf7","tid":738520,"uid":173932,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T14:49:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ab4a5643ea37573f9537580db1c0728b236d496a","tid":738520,"uid":191755,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T15:26:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"92ea425b8c0f10677f592b450348fbbb5b8dcc27","tid":738520,"uid":135879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T15:51:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d45787bea3b1217209402f68d81af8b312a1d625","tid":738520,"uid":187975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T15:54:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d0fd9a6beda30308a47c85d1e749e63ad90bd365","tid":738520,"uid":186866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T16:47:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d2355179ba52dc022417817dbd59edaf122b7088","tid":738520,"uid":54396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T10:00:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3e0995aa37bbc23953353208a7a88dad093c9510","tid":738520,"uid":171755